### 1 Create a new resource
POST http://localhost:3000/api/resources
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Resource",
  "description": "This is a sample resource"
}

### 2️ List all resources
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources

### 3️ Get resource details by ID
# Replace `PUT_RESOURCE_ID_HERE` with the actual resource ID.
GET http://localhost:3000/api/resources/PUT_RESOURCE_ID_HERE

### 4️ Update a resource
# Updates an existing resource by ID.
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/resources/PUT_RESOURCE_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Resource",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### 5️ Delete a resource
# Deletes a resource by ID.
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/resources/PUT_RESOURCE_ID_HERE
